$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT {
  coords 299.133 21.07 5642.152
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2>"\
  "DTL: 24/07/2013, 1300hr, Al-Hadra, Iraq."\
  "Weather: Clear, no forecast of change, sightlines 1km+"\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2>"\
  "Large parts of Iraq have fallen into chaos as insurgent groups continue to seize territory across the region. Iraqi forces, weakened by years of fighting and heavy losses in both men and equipment, have struggled to contain the growing insurgency."\
  "North of Al-Hadra, a key highway checkpoint remains under Iraqi control, disrupting insurgent movement through the area. Intelligence reports indicate a large insurgent force is preparing to attack and eliminate the garrison stationed there in order to secure unrestricted access along the highway."\
  "The checkpoint is isolated and expected to come under heavy assault. Both sides understand the importance of the position — whoever controls the highway controls movement through the region."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CS {
  coords 299.133 21.07 5642.152
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• HQ - Briza-21"\
  "• 1st Squad - Briza-22"\
  "• 2nd Squad - Briza-23"\
  "• 3rd Squad - Briza-24"\
  "• 4th Squad - Briza-25"\
  "• 5th Squad - Briza-26"\
  "• 6th Squad - Briza-27"\
  "• 7th Squad - Briza-28"\
  ""\
  "<h2>FREQ/CHAN</h2>"\
  "• All callsigns - 42Hz"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 EF {
  coords 299.133 21.07 5642.152
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "Enemy forces consist of regular Iraqi light infantry, approximately 25 personnel strong, currently garrisoning the fortified northern checkpoint at GRID: 038069.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• The checkpoint is heavily fortified, featuring high HESCO walls, manned tower bunkers along the perimeter, and razor wire covering both road entrances. Additional fortified fighting positions are established throughout the compound, on surrounding buildings, and along the access road.  "\
  "Weapon systems include NSV, KORD, PKM, a single mortar, and Kornet ATGM positions, all sighted to cover the surrounding terrain. Iraqi forces regularly rotate weapon placements, making patterns difficult to predict.  "\
  "The checkpoint maintains clear all-round observation, with minimal cover or concealment within 300 metres.  "\
  "• 2x .50 cal Humvees have been identified and are used for defence, transport, and general duties around the checkpoint.  "\
  "• Enemy forces are expected to be well armed and well supplied with ammunition. The checkpoint was last attacked the previous month and has since had time to rearm and reinforce."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FF {
  coords 299.133 21.07 5642.152
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>  "\
  "We are the fighters of Briza Troop, Sundown Company.  "\
  "Our force consists of approximately 50 personnel currently located within the city of Al-Hadra at GRID: 039043, with an additional 14 fighters en route.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>  "\
  "• 1x BRDM (seperate from the rest of vehicles) with explosives for use as a VBIED. One volunteer will be selected for the attack.  "\
  "The driver may detonate the explosives manually from the dashboard or enable a deadman’s switch.  "\
  "• We possess a range of armed vehicles, including:  "\
  "1x BMP-1  "\
  "1x captured armoured Humvee fitted with a BTR turret  "\
  "2x soft-skin PKM UAZs  "\
  "1x captured soft-skin .50 cal Humvee  "\
  "1x 7.62 front-mounted technical  "\
  ""\
  "We also have:  "\
  "1x unarmed M113  "\
  "1x unarmed armoured Humvee  "\
  "2x unarmed BRDMs"\
  ""\
  "<h2>SERVICE & SUPPORT</h2>  "\
  "• 14 additional fighters are currently moving toward the staging area. They will reinforce our numbers if casualties are sustained.  "\
  "• We have access to approximately 30 motorcycles and 20 civilian vehicles for transport, from cars, wagons, and trucks."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 MIS {
  coords 299.133 21.07 5642.152
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>  "\
  "We are to conduct a DELIBERATE ASSAULT on the Iraqi checkpoint in order to SECURE it by OCCUPYING the position and DESTROYING the garrisoned forces.  "\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISSION DESCRIPTION</h2>  "\
  "Securing this checkpoint is critical to our freedom of movement within the region. Its capture will open the northern highway in and out of Al-Hadra, allowing the movement of men, vehicles, and supplies through the area.  "\
  ""\
  "We shall without fear assault into the checkpoint, occupy it with our presence within the perminter, and destroy the Iraqi troops by slaughtering them, mashallah!\""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_INSURGENT"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}